      "type": "text",
      "x": 1630,
      "y": 890,
      "width": 208.79999999999998,
      "height": 178.20000000000002,
      "text": "O dev só diz:\n\"Corrige a CAN-123.\"\n\nA skill já sabe:\n• Projeto: CAN\n• Cloud ID: configurado\n• Instância Atlas: configurada\n\nTrigger automático: o agente\ndetecta \"CAN-NNN\" e carrega\na skill automaticamente.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
